    "## Open Research Directions\n",
    "\n",
    "The instantiation of the lighthouse loop (@sec-running-the-loop) demonstrates a bounded, rejectable turn, but automating this process at scale exposes profound, unsolved challenges in systems research. Resolving these challenges requires thesis-scale advances in learning, verification, and cryptography.\n",
